Package graph

This package defines an interface for graphs (in Graph). An implementation, using adjacency lists (implemented using Hashtables) is provided in AdjacencyGraph. An interface for traversing graphs (as a subclass of the Graph interface) is provided in Traversal. Since this is a subclass of Graph, a Traversal object will also be a Graph object. I.e., a Traversal object does not need to be provided with a graph to traverse, the traversal object is itself the graph that must be traversed. No implementations of Traversal is provided. These are left as an exercise.
